Synopsis

Basically, this could very well have been the book Einstein
would have written, had he had the time to do so.
It shows how the Grand Universal Theory is more like a
Generic Underlying Tapestry, that shows up in multiple
aspects of reality. That, and the concept of Infinite Multiple
Realities make this 77 page illustrated book an interesting read.



Infinity Plus One,
By: Sander Beals
Language: EN
Format: PDF
Pages: 77
